I told you before,
I don't like it when they go down.

607
00:50:49,842 --> 00:50:52,719
I used to have another broker.

608
00:50:52,928 --> 00:50:55,848
He bought stocks for me
that went down.

609
00:50:56,098 --> 00:50:58,517
