- What are you saying?

753
01:02:13,025 --> 01:02:16,195
Vic has great instincts about people.

754
01:02:18,071 --> 01:02:21,742
He saw you where? Grand Central?

755
01:02:22,993 --> 01:02:27,080
- It was a setup?
- "Setup" is so negative.

756
01:02:27,331 --> 01:02:30,167
